    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This works!\n\nMarkup.\n`<form action=\"#\" id=\"ios-hide-keyboard-on-submit\" >\n      <input id=\"search-box\"  type=\"search\"/>\n    </form>`\n`\nJs to prevent form from submitting and closing keyboard.\n\n`var iosForm = document.getElementById('ios-hide-keyboard-on-submit');\n    iosForm.onsubmit = function(e){\n      e.preventDefault();\n      var inputField = document.activeElement;\n      inputField.blur();\n    };`\n\nAs it is now, it will trigger blur on desktop as well, which might not be wanted. Thank you for the good feedback and for this great application. Without you this would't be as smooth to make as it was: https://www.vingruppen.no/produkter\n",
    "created_at": "2016-11-08T11:59:46Z",
